Homer's Odysses. Translated according to ye Greeke by. Geo: Chapman Odyssey. Book 1-24. English. Chapman Homer. Chapman, George, 1559?-1634.
[10], 194, [2], 195-376, [2] p.
By Rich: Field [and W. Jaggard], for Nathaniell Butter, Imprinted at London : [1615?]
Another issue, adding books 13-24, of the 1614 edition which includes only books 1-12. In verse. Printer's name supplied and publication date conjectured by STC. The title page is engraved. A cancel letterpress title page is occasionally found, but properly belongs with STC 13624.5.--STC. Imperfect; lacks leaf R8. Reproduction of the original in the Bodleian Library.
